msgid "# Dynamic Batch"
msgstr "# 动态批处理"

msgid ""
"Dynamic batch is a technique that dynamically adjusts the chunksize during "
"each inference iteration within the chunked prefilling strategy according to"
" the resources and SLO targets, thereby improving the effective throughput "
"and decreasing the TBT."
msgstr "动态批处理是一种在分块预填充策略中，根据资源和SLO目标，在每次推理迭代期间动态调整块大小的技术，从而提升有效吞吐量并降低TBT。"

msgid ""
"Dynamic batch is controlled by the value of the `--SLO_limits_for_dynamic_batch`.\n"
"Notably, only Atlas A2 inference products are supported with decode token number scales below 2048 so far.\n"
"Especially, the improvements are quite obvious on Qwen, Llama models.\n"
"We are working on further improvements and this feature will support more XPUs in the future."
msgstr ""
"动态批处理由 `--SLO_limits_for_dynamic_batch` 的值控制。\n"
"值得注意的是，目前仅支持 Atlas A2 推理产品，且解码 token 数量规模需低于 2048。\n"
"特别是在 Qwen、Llama 模型上，性能提升非常明显。\n"
"我们正在持续改进，未来该功能将支持更多 XPU。"

msgid "## Getting started"
msgstr "## 快速开始"

msgid "### Prerequisites"
msgstr "### 前提条件"

msgid ""
"1. Dynamic batch now depends on an offline cost model saved in a lookup "
"table to refine the token budget. The lookup table is saved in a '.csv' "
"file, which should be first downloaded from [A2-B3-BLK128.csv](https://vllm-"
"ascend.obs.cn-north-4.myhuaweicloud.com/vllm-"
"ascend/dynamic_batch_scheduler/A2-B3-BLK128.csv), renamed, and saved to the "
"path `vllm_ascend/core/profile_table.csv`"
msgstr ""
"1. 动态批处理目前依赖于保存在查找表中的离线成本模型来优化 token 预算。查找表保存在 '.csv' 文件中，需先从 "
"[A2-B3-BLK128.csv](https://vllm-ascend.obs.cn-"
"north-4.myhuaweicloud.com/vllm-"
"ascend/dynamic_batch_scheduler/A2-B3-BLK128.csv) 下载，重命名后保存至路径 "
"`vllm_ascend/core/profile_table.csv`"

msgid ""
"2. `Pandas` is needed to load the lookup table, in case pandas is not "
"installed."
msgstr "2. 需要 `Pandas` 来加载查找表，以防未安装 pandas。"

msgid "### Tuning Parameters"
msgstr "### 调优参数"

msgid ""
"`--SLO_limits_for_dynamic_batch` is the tuning parameter (integer type) for "
"the dynamic batch feature, larger values relax latency limitation, leading "
"to higher effective throughput. The parameter can be selected according to "
"the specific models or service requirements."
msgstr ""
"`--SLO_limits_for_dynamic_batch` "
"是动态批处理功能的调优参数（整数类型），值越大，延迟限制越宽松，有效吞吐量越高。可根据具体模型或服务需求选择该参数。"

msgid "### Supported Models"
msgstr "### 支持的模型"

msgid ""
"So far, dynamic batch performs better on several dense models including Qwen"
" and Llama (from 8B to 32B) with `tensor_parallel_size=8`. For different "
"models, a proper `SLO_limits_for_dynamic_batch` parameter is needed. The "
"empirical value of this parameter is generally `35, 50, or 75`. Therefore, "
"some additional tests are needed to select the best parameter."
msgstr ""
"目前，动态批处理在多个稠密模型上表现更佳，包括 Qwen 和 Llama（8B 至 32B），且 "
"`tensor_parallel_size=8`。对于不同模型，需要设置合适的 `SLO_limits_for_dynamic_batch` "
"参数。该参数的经验值通常为 `35、50 或 75`。因此，需要进行一些额外测试以选择最佳参数。"

